text: The Dancing House () is the nickname of the Nationale-Nederlanden building on the Rašínovo nábřeží in Prague, Czech Republic. It was designed by the Croatian-Czech architect Vlado Milunić with architect Frank Gehry in 1992.Nationale-Nederlanden Building Frank O. Gehry, The Architect's Studio.
